Name: Starship Wars
About the game: Add to your wish list!! A great power war is going on, fight for victory!! Game features Play in 3 different game modes, an Infinite Mode to challenge your abilities, an Adventure Mode with 30 levels to challenge your skills and a Survival Mode to challenge your stamina. Defeat several different bosses and enemies. Extremely accurate controls. Use over 70 different shots to defeat your enemies. Buy powerful ships, special shots and mini ships to help you in battle and get a high score. Gameplay - Move in all four directions to dodge enemies and enemy shots, destroy all bosses, enemies and everything you see ahead, collect crystals to spend in the store, grab upgrades to strengthen your shots and mini ships to help you in battle.
